# Spaceflux Ltd

> UK space domain awareness company providing AI-driven tracking and mapping of space objects via a proprietary optical sensor network.

## What they do

Founded in 2022, Spaceflux addresses space congestion by deploying a proprietary optical sensor network combined with an AI analytics platform to track and characterise space objects. Their customers include satellite operators, governments, and the insurance industry.

## Products and solutions

- **Space object tracking platform** - AI-driven analytics derived from optical sensor data, providing tracking, mapping, and behavioural characterisation of objects in orbit.

